questions.quote: Hey, whatever it is, I am sure it has happened to me. Y'know, actually once-once I got dumped during sex.
I do-I do not have a boyfriend. There's a guy in one of my classes who-who has a crush on me.
Hurry! Monica's gonna make you pack! She's got jobs for everyone! Now, it's too late for me, but save your selves!
Okay! Okay! Okay! You win! You win!! I can't have sex with ya!
Anyway, I figured after work I'd go pick up a bottle of wine, go over there and, uh, try to woo her.
No! No! I just went to pick up Phoebe Buffay's checks; there were a lot of them.
